ntence\": \"Hoffman accomplished the feat by the skin of her teeth as she made the 40-entry cutoff at the 39th spot, collecting just enough points to advance.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.956907867865091e-13, \"text\": \"Hoffman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a tight battle in the women's 400m hurdles, with 32 athletes hitting the qualifying standard and just eight making it through by world rankings position to complete the field.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Robyn Brown, who ruled the event for the Philippines in the Asian Athletics Championships last year, fell short after ending up at 53rd.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robyn\", \"score\": 0.9999995329957254, \"rank\": 3.651218447328383e-07, \"text\": \"Robyn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robyn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robyn\"}, {\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9997261291535753, \"rank\": 0.00014257438074755696, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1070, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999965938901624, \"rank\": 3.406121320275154e-06, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Tolentino - a Filipino residing in Spain - clinched his Olympic seat with hardly any scare as he finished 30th out of 40 qualifiers in the men's 110m hurdles.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1194, \"end\": 1199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9974406806442787, \"rank\": 0.002511688036424038, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hoffman and Tolentino raised the number of Filipino track and field athletes who will see action in Paris to three, with pole vaulterEJ Obienaleading the pack as one of the Philippines' strongest medal bets.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.956907867865091e-13, \"text\": \"Hoffman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trevor_Hoffman\"}, {\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tolentino\", \"score\": 0.9994176670559343, \"rank\": 0.0005826119380966179, \"text\": \"Tolentino\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tolentino\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tolentino\"}, {\"begin\": 1419, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999411861626, \"rank\": 5.8813766103193645e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1492, \"end\": 1503, \"title\": \"http